                    </view>
                    <view class="down">￥ 价值300元（50元/本，共六期）</view>
                </view>
                <view class="each-limits">
                    <view class="up">
                        <image class="img" src="/assets/img/icon/ticket.png" mode="aspectFill" />
                        <view class="text">全年观看最务实、全干货的“走进名企学管会”系列直播节目，</view>
                    </view>
                    <view class="down">￥ 价值478元（39.9/场，共12场）</view>
                </view>
                <view class="each-limits">
                    <view class="up">
                        <image class="img" src="/assets/img/icon/ticket.png" mode="aspectFill" />
